      <body>You'll see this error if your mailserver has an SSL certificate set up for a hostname other than the one to which you are trying to connect.  I was experiencing the same error, until I changed my smtp_settings to reflect the hostname of the associated SSL cert.</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;You'll see this error if your mailserver has an SSL certificate
set up for a hostname other than the one to which you are trying to
connect. I was experiencing the same error, until I changed my
smtp_settings to reflect the hostname of the associated SSL
cert.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
